{"tid":2453490,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG Defi Project 經投票後正式採用Lennon 連農場做Project名","createTime":"2021-03-19T13:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T13:05:52.000Z","uid":159795,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"abd695f515c8c48bd3293041502aad67148c5db2","tid":2453490,"uid":159795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T13:20:27.000Z","msg":"多謝大家既投票，我地到9點為止總共收到100票。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n26票投左比Harvest Moon 牧場物語，74票投左比Lennon 連農場。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以LIHKG Defi Project會採用Lennon 連農場作為之後既名 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家請期待我地下次update。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n投票post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2452030/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2452030/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866c98d82324925bfbbf1aeace37b2b74e14b9a9","tid":2453490,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T13:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fde530e59026fd7d6ab4190bb52858b09c52d04","tid":2453490,"uid":320985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}